casebody.data:
Hugh WINFREY v. UNITED STATES. No. 402. Circuit Court of Appeals, Tenth Circuit. Jan. 28, 1931. S. R. Owens, of Denver, Colo., for appellant. Ralph L. Carr, U. S. Atty., of Denver, Colo.

Before LEWIS, PHILLIPS, and Mc-DERMOTT, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Case remanded January 28, 1931, pursuant to stipulation, with direction to vacate the judgment and grant a new trial.
